{"title": "Naháč od Berniniho", "content": "<p><i><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">Nikdy</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;nelžetě&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">ženě</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">protože</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;v&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">každé ženě</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;je&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">kus agenta FBI</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">kus</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #5f6368; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;\">psychopata</span><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #4d5156; font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;a&nbs